  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t夏日炎炎，热浪滚滚，面对一个如此容易使人心浮气躁的季节，你有什么避暑好招吗？</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;The film (500) Days of Summer always gives me a brisk feeling about relationship, but when it comes to the real summer, here comes the uneasy feelings from heat, sweat, and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sunstroke\" target=\"_blank\">sunstroke</a>. I am now studying at Wuhan City, one of &quot;the Three Hot Stoves&quot;, where summer days without air conditioners at dormitories are horrible. Therefore, methods to avoid sunstroke are indispensible.<br />\n\tThe most useful method is to take a cold water shower. It sweeps the sweat all over your body and eases the uncomfortable feeling of hot air. Back to the days when our dormitories were not equipped with air conditioners, it was almost impossible for one not to be woken up by heat at night. In order to fall asleep after the heat interruption, we often have to take several showers a night. Another way is to eat fruits like watermelon. Not only will they provide us with water, but they offer mineral substance as well.<br />\n\tIn fact, since the application of air conditioners on the campus, summer days are not a